title: ONE CALL

description.plain:
“One Call” serves as Rich Amiri’s breakout single of 2023. It serves as the last track released before album, the track was not supposed to be released as a single, but it was released on November 3 due to the postponement of Ghetto Fabulous.

Five days after release, the song got an official music video that was directed by NeveFilms. Additionally, the track blew up on TikTok helping elevate Amiri’s name within the music industry.

During the tracking week ending February 17, 2024, the song reached a peak of #64 on the Hot 100. The song marked his first solo appearance on the chart. On top of that, the track was awarded with the RIAA platinum award on August 13th, 2024, marking it as his first official certification.
